      "medicalSpecialty: always keep as Dentistry for dental practices",
      "@id: always append /#dentist to the homepage URL",
      "sameAs: collect ALL links — Google Maps, Facebook, Instagram, Yelp, Healthgrades, Zocdoc, CareCredit, ZocDoc, and any other directory or social media link found anywhere on the site including footer — add as many as found",
