      "review: include ALL reviews visible on the homepage — add as many review entries as found — do not limit to the number of placeholders in the template",
      "founder: include ALL doctors mentioned on the homepage or about page — add as many entries as found",
      "priceRange: use $$ as default for dental practices unless site specifies otherwise",
      "paymentAccepted: list every insurance plan and payment method mentioned anywhere on the site including footer and insurance section",
      "aggregateRating.ratingValue: get from Google review widget or review section on homepage",
      "aggregateRating.reviewCount: get the total number shown on the homepage review section — use the highest total count visible",
      "review: include ALL reviews visible on the homepage — do not skip any — copy author name and review text exactly as shown",
      "hasOfferCatalog: include ALL services listed in the navigation menu and homepage service section — add as many Offer items as needed, do not limit to the number of placeholders in the template",
      "address: copy exact address from the website — check footer, contact page, and Google Maps link",
      "geo: get exact latitude and longitude from the Google Maps link on the site — never estimate",
      "openingHoursSpecification: get hours from the footer or contact page — REMOVE any day that is closed, never use 00:00 for closed days",
      "EXPAND RULE: for any array field like sameAs, areaServed, review, founder, openingHoursSpecification, and hasOfferCatalog — always add as many entries as data exists on the site, never cut short",
      "NO PLACEHOLDERS: the final output must have zero placeholders — every field must contain real data or be removed entirely",
      "VALIDATE: before finalizing, check that all URLs are real and working, all phone numbers match, all addresses match Google Maps, geo coordinates match the Google Maps pin"
    ]
